          "body": "Tracks: #3\n\nTracks: #3\n\n## Context\n\nParent feature-request: #3 (https://github.com/ConcaveTrillion/pd-book-tools/issues/3)\n\nThis spec issue tracks the design + decomposition of the parent feature-request via:\n\n1. `/spec-from-issue 277940NEW` — produces `docs/specs/NN-<slug>.md` (the design spec) + draft PR.\n2. `/decompose-spec docs/specs/NN-<slug>.md` — creates per-spec milestone + child issues with `bot:ship-issue-ready` where appropriate.\n\n## Triage decision\n\nApproved as needing-spec during the 2026-05-11 backlog triage sweep — this feature requires design work before implementation; not a one-PR tracking-style chore.\n\nInherits effort/model labels from the parent feature-request.\n\nSpec: (to be filled by /spec-from-issue)\n",
